---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Mario Tarosso" description="About Mario Tarosso Lorem Ipsum">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/portrait.jpg"
					alt="Mario Tarosso at work with a colleague"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						As a versatile software developer with expertise in web development, game development, and content creation, I am constantly seeking new challenges and opportunities to showcase my skills. With a strong foundation in both front-end and back-end development, I am comfortable working with a diverse range of technologies and frameworks. My passion for coding extends beyond traditional web applications, as I have delved into the captivating world of game development, creating immersive and engaging experiences for players. Additionally, I have embraced the role of an educator by producing educational YouTube videos focused on game development, sharing my knowledge and empowering others to explore this exciting field.
					</p>
                    <br />
					<p>
						I am a lifelong learner, consistently striving to improve my skills and stay up-to-date with the latest industry trends in software development. By combining my technical expertise with a creative mindset, I am able to deliver innovative solutions and captivating user experiences. If you're curious to see some of my past projects and witness my abilities as a developer, please feel free to explore my GitHub profile.
					</p>
                    <br />
					<p>
						With my comprehensive background in software development, game development, and educational content creation, I am excited to bring my diverse skill set to any project or opportunity that comes my way. Let's connect and embark on a journey of creativity, learning, and impactful software development.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>UNOPAR - Universidade Norte do Paran√°</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>Computer Science</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>Google Developer Scholarship</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>Laravel Certification</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Unreal Engine</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>Vue Js</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>Unity</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>HTML</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>CSS</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>JavaScript</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>PHP</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>MySQL</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>Laravel</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
